Description
--The table contains information about trucks including their identification, specifications, and operational details. It includes data such as the make, model year, acquisition date, and fuel type. This table can be useful for fleet management, monitoring vehicle status, and analyzing trends in acquisitions and usage.

COLUMN                   |             TYPE             |          COMMENT
truck_id                 |            string            |
UNIT_NUMBER              |            BIGINT            |
MAKE                     |            string            |
MODEL_YEAR               |            BIGINT            |
VIN                      |            string            |
acquisition_date         |            DATE              |
acquisition_MILEAGE      |            BIGINT            |
FUEL_TYPE                |            STRING            |
TANK_CAPACITY_GALLONS    |            BIGINT            |
STATUS                   |            STRING            |
HOME TERMINAL            |            STRING            |


---SAMPLE DATA :
What are the counts of trucks by make?
--SQL:
      SELECT `make`, COUNT(*) AS count
FROM `datawerhouse1`.`bronze`.`trucks`
GROUP BY `make`
ORDER BY count DESC;
--RESULT:
      make	   count
   Peterbilt	   24
 Freightliner 	 22
    Mack	       21
    Volvo	       20
International	   18
  Kenworth	     15
